definition: variant of 嘍囉|喽啰[lou2 luo5]
(final particle equivalent to 了[le5])/(particle calling attention to, or mildly warning of, a situation)

sentences.english: The mighty Archimonde also empowered agents of his own.
sentences.chinese: 強大的阿克蒙德也爲自己找到了嘍羅。

sentences.english: A born warrior couldn't stay working as a smalltime enforcer for long.
sentences.chinese: 一個天生的勇士不可能長時間安於做一個小嘍羅。
